i have met this problem also....
finally, i find when use Key_Shared subscription mode, the producer must set like this:
`   private Producer<Integer> createProducer(String topic, boolean enableBatch) throws PulsarClientException {
        Producer<Integer> producer = null;
        if (enableBatch) {
            producer = pulsarClient.newProducer(Schema.INT32)
                    .topic(topic)
                    .enableBatching(true)
                    .batcherBuilder(BatcherBuilder.KEY_BASED)
                    .create();
        } else {
            producer = pulsarClient.newProducer(Schema.INT32)
                    .topic(topic)
                    .enableBatching(false)
                    .create();
        }
        return producer;
    }`
because producer enable batching by default, so you must set batcherBuilder(BatcherBuilder.KEY_BASED) when use Key_Shared mode.
